  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Go forth, it is you who will save the universes... from annihilation.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/b4e2f40d6c26797d5375b3887d2b1eba.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi: Starbound Saga is a 2D platformer with gameplay styles inspired by the Kirby and Sonic series. With Cappi, use powerful abilities and maintain speed to be able to save the galaxy in record time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/e3d96d7651603659397beacb05d495b0.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ea05f798f004c3ae0389c3ea28f902b0.webp?t=1753070414\" width=60 height=60 /></span>Cappi Starr is a young star traveler who wishes to speed through the galaxy carefree someday.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/e508cf0279b92b4e08249e1a98c133a7.webp?t=1753070414\" width=48 height=48 /></span>Atlas Zan is an intergalactic geologist traveling with Cappi to learn more of the worlds and remind Cappi of his duty as a Hero of Light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/7c9eca6b6de91bed0b76549b876b3854.webp?t=1753070414\" width=60 height=60 /></span>Ruv Hector Drevalin is a wandering swordsman hanging with Cappi to uphold his motto of keeping justice in the galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/4aff4f15c95c0b36723f9fefaa83ef80.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi is very versatile and diverse in his kit and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi is equipped at all times with his trusty <strong>Prism</strong> <strong>Yoyo</strong>. He can swing it <strong>horizontally and vertically</strong> to catch foes high and low. Cappi also can stomp on the ground to attack foes relentlessly or to catch his bearings. It can also be used to go down slopes to gain great speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to this, Cappi and use the abilities of defeated enemies to power up his yoyo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using these abilities, his damage, moveset and mobility get an upgrade or are completely new! Use the abilities to your advantage to mow down the Cursed and make it to the goal quickly and easily!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Go forth, it is you who will save the universes... from annihilation.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/b4e2f40d6c26797d5375b3887d2b1eba.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi: Starbound Saga is a 2D platformer with gameplay styles inspired by the Kirby and Sonic series. With Cappi, use powerful abilities and maintain speed to be able to save the galaxy in record time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/e3d96d7651603659397beacb05d495b0.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ea05f798f004c3ae0389c3ea28f902b0.webp?t=1753070414\" width=60 height=60 /></span>Cappi Starr is a young star traveler who wishes to speed through the galaxy carefree someday.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/e508cf0279b92b4e08249e1a98c133a7.webp?t=1753070414\" width=48 height=48 /></span>Atlas Zan is an intergalactic geologist traveling with Cappi to learn more of the worlds and remind Cappi of his duty as a Hero of Light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/7c9eca6b6de91bed0b76549b876b3854.webp?t=1753070414\" width=60 height=60 /></span>Ruv Hector Drevalin is a wandering swordsman hanging with Cappi to uphold his motto of keeping justice in the galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/4aff4f15c95c0b36723f9fefaa83ef80.avif?t=1753070414\" width=717 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi is very versatile and diverse in his kit and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/fb93b03e5f97761316febdea6f52f351.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cappi is equipped at all times with his trusty <strong>Prism</strong> <strong>Yoyo</strong>. He can swing it <strong>horizontally and vertically</strong> to catch foes high and low. Cappi also can stomp on the ground to attack foes relentlessly or to catch his bearings. It can also be used to go down slopes to gain great speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/c8187ce4ac29c4c6a5b747fb7ff9959c.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to this, Cappi and use the abilities of defeated enemies to power up his yoyo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.poster.avif?t=1753070414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.webm?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/6e0ac9594af0d31c7dcceddfce385671.mp4?t=1753070414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using these abilities, his damage, moveset and mobility get an upgrade or are completely new! Use the abilities to your advantage to mow down the Cursed and make it to the goal quickly and easily!</p>",
